fields.name: Barbell Bench Press
fields.description: Lie on a flat bench and lower the barbell to your chest, then press it back up to full arm extension.

fields.name: Incline Dumbbell Press
fields.description: Press dumbbells upward on an inclined bench to target the upper chest.

fields.name: Decline Bench Press
fields.description: Press the barbell on a decline bench to emphasize the lower chest.

fields.name: Push-Ups
fields.description: Classic bodyweight exercise performed in a plank position, lowering and raising your body.

fields.name: Dumbbell Flyes
fields.description: Lie on a bench and lower dumbbells out to the sides in an arc motion, stretching the chest.

fields.name: Cable Crossover
fields.description: Pull cable handles across your body in a hugging motion to isolate the chest.

fields.name: Barbell Squat
fields.description: Lower your body by bending knees and hips with a barbell on your back, then return to standing.

fields.name: Romanian Deadlift
fields.description: Hinge at the hips while keeping legs mostly straight to lower the barbell, targeting hamstrings.

fields.name: Leg Press
fields.description: Push weight away using your legs while seated in a leg press machine.

fields.name: Leg Curl
fields.description: Curl your legs upward against resistance to isolate the hamstrings.

fields.name: Leg Extension
fields.description: Extend your legs against resistance to isolate the quadriceps.

fields.name: Walking Lunges
fields.description: Step forward into a lunge position alternating legs while walking.

fields.name: Calf Raises
fields.description: Raise your heels off the ground to work the calf muscles.

fields.name: Pull-Ups
fields.description: Hang from a bar and pull your body upward until your chin is over the bar.

fields.name: Lat Pulldown
fields.description: Pull a bar down to your chest while seated, engaging the back muscles.

fields.name: Barbell Row
fields.description: Bend forward and pull a barbell toward your torso, squeezing your back muscles.

fields.name: Dumbbell Row
fields.description: Support yourself on a bench and pull a dumbbell toward your hip.

fields.name: Face Pulls
fields.description: Pull a rope attachment toward your face, engaging rear delts and upper back.

fields.name: Deadlift
fields.description: Lift a barbell from the ground to hip level by extending hips and knees.

fields.name: Overhead Press
fields.description: Press a barbell overhead from shoulder level to full arm extension.

fields.name: Dumbbell Shoulder Press
fields.description: Press dumbbells overhead from shoulder height.

fields.name: Lateral Raises
fields.description: Raise dumbbells out to the sides to isolate the lateral deltoids.

fields.name: Front Raises
fields.description: Raise dumbbells in front of you to shoulder height.

fields.name: Barbell Curl
fields.description: Curl a barbell upward by flexing the elbows, keeping upper arms stationary.

fields.name: Dumbbell Curl
fields.description: Curl dumbbells upward alternating or simultaneously.

fields.name: Hammer Curl
fields.description: Curl dumbbells with palms facing each other to target biceps and forearms.

fields.name: Preacher Curl
fields.description: Perform curls with arms resting on a preacher bench for strict isolation.

fields.name: Tricep Dips
fields.description: Lower and raise your body between parallel bars using tricep strength.

fields.name: Tricep Pushdown
fields.description: Push a cable attachment downward to extend the elbows and work the triceps.

fields.name: Overhead Tricep Extension
fields.description: Extend a dumbbell overhead, focusing on tricep contraction.

fields.name: Skull Crushers
fields.description: Lower a barbell toward your forehead while lying on a bench, then extend back up.

fields.name: Plank
fields.description: Hold a push-up position with body straight, engaging core muscles.

fields.name: Crunches
fields.description: Lie on your back and curl your upper body toward your knees.

fields.name: Russian Twists
fields.description: Sit with feet elevated and rotate your torso side to side.

fields.name: Hanging Leg Raises
fields.description: Hang from a bar and raise your legs to work the lower abs.

fields.name: Cable Woodchoppers
fields.description: Rotate your torso while pulling a cable across your body in a chopping motion.

fields.name: Bicycle Crunches
fields.description: Alternate bringing opposite elbow to knee in a cycling motion.

fields.name: Mountain Climbers
fields.description: In plank position, alternate driving knees toward chest rapidly.

fields.name: Burpees
fields.description: Drop to push-up, jump feet forward, then jump up explosively.

fields.name: Kettlebell Swings
fields.description: Swing a kettlebell between legs and up to chest level using hip thrust.

fields.name: Box Jumps
fields.description: Jump explosively onto a raised platform and step back down.

fields.name: Battle Rope Waves
fields.description: Create waves in heavy ropes using alternating or simultaneous arm movements.

fields.name: Farmer's Walk
fields.description: Walk while holding heavy weights at your sides, maintaining posture.

fields.name: Shrugs
fields.description: Elevate your shoulders toward your ears while holding weights.

fields.name: Hip Thrusts
fields.description: Thrust hips upward with upper back on bench and weight across hips.

fields.name: Bulgarian Split Squat
fields.description: Perform single-leg squats with rear foot elevated on bench.

fields.name: TRX Rows
fields.description: Pull your body toward handles while leaning back in TRX straps.

fields.name: Cable Rows
fields.description: Pull cable handle toward torso while seated, squeezing shoulder blades.
